briefdescription.para: I2C driver implementation for the EUSCI controller on MSP432.

detaileddescription.para: This I2C driver implementation is designed to operate on a EUCSI controller in I2C mode. The I2CMSP432 header file should be included in an application as follows: #include<ti/drivers/I2C.h> #include<ti/drivers/I2CMSP432.h>
Refer to I2C.h for a complete description of APIs & example of use.
